## Status  
Accepted  
  
## Context  
We will maintain Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) for this project.  
Each ADR captures a significant architectural choice, along with the  
context, decision, and consequences.  
  
## Decision  
We will store ADRs in Markdown format inside the  
`architecture_decision_records/` directory. New records will be created  
using standardized templates.  
  
## Consequences  
- Architectural decisions become explicit.  
- Changes affecting architecture must be documented.  
- The team gains a clear, chronological record of design evolution.